headline: Is Merck Still Attractive at $106 After Recent Gains and Pipeline Progress?
summary: Wondering if Merck at around $106 is still a smart buy or if most of the upside is already priced in? This breakdown will help you decide whether the market is being too cautious or not cautious enough. Despite a flat return year to date and a modest 1.6% gain over three years, the stock has climbed 6.7% in the last month and 11.4% over the past year, hinting that sentiment around Merck's long term prospects is quietly improving.
